data.description:
Welcome to 9758 Laredo St. #26b, where contemporary comfort meets urban convenience. This exceptional 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom townhome is your ticket to a lifestyle of style, ease, and accessibility in the heart of Commerce City.

Key Features:
Bedrooms: 3
Bathrooms: 2.5
Parking: Attached 2-car Garage

Modern Luxury Awaits:
Step inside and be embraced by an inviting and well-designed living space. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, offering an ideal space for entertaining guests or savoring quality family time.

Community Delights:
Enjoy the fantastic amenities of this well-maintained community, including a refreshing pool to beat the summer heat, a playground for outdoor fun, and a clubhouse for social gatherings.

Attached Garage:
The attached 2-car garage provides convenience and additional storage space, ensuring your vehicle and belongings are kept secure.

Prime Location:
Nestled in a highly desirable Commerce City neighborhood, you'll enjoy the perfect blend of suburban tranquility and urban accessibility. Parks, schools, shopping, dining, and entertainment options are all within easy reach.

Don't miss the opportunity to make 9758 Laredo St. #26b your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience modern living in Commerce City.
